UmojanCommandCenter.Description:
Primary structure. Used to receive gathered resources. Can use the Warp to Location ability.

Enables:
- MCSs
UmojanCommandCenter.Name: Command Hub

UmojanMCS.Description:
Basic worker unit. Can gather resources, build Umojan structures, and repair.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanMCS.Name: MCS

UmojanRefinery.Description: Built over a Vespene Geyser to allow harvesting of vespene gas.
UmojanRefinery.Name: Distillery

UmojanSupplyCache.Description:
Provides supply.
Supply allows you to create more units.
Supply Cache can be lowered to allow units to walk over them.

Can be upgraded to provide Power Levels.
UmojanSupplyCache.Name: Supply Cache

UmojanSupplyCacheLowered.Description:
Provides supply.
Supply allows you to create more units.
Supply Cache can be lowered to allow units to walk over them.

Can be upgraded to provide Power Levels.
UmojanSupplyCacheLowered.Name: Supply Cache

UmojanEnergyGenerator.Description:
Provides power and supply.
Supply allows you to create more units.
Power increase nearby structure production speed and grant them a shield.
UmojanEnergyGenerator.Name: Energy Generator

UmojanBarracks.Description:
Infantry-production facility.

Enables:
- Pretorian
- Commando
- Bunkers from MCSs
- Science Facilities from MCSs
- Shadow Ops at the MCSs
- Workshop at the MCSs
UmojanBarracks.Name: Academy

UmojanMarine.Description:
General-purpose infantry.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanMarine.Name: Pretorian

UmojanCommando.Description:
Raider. Can jump up and down cliffs. Regenerates life quickly while out of combat. Can use KD8 Charge.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanCommando.Name: Commando

UmojanPlasmabat.Description:
Heavy close combat anti-armor assault infantry, can use Corrosive Blast.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanPlasmabat.Name: Plasmabat

UmojanDisruptor.Description:
Support robot. Can use Transfer Shield Power, can be upgraded to use Disruption Web

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanDisruptor.Name: Harmoniser

UmojanShadowguard.Description:
Infiltration unit. Can use Snipe and Cloak abilities. Can also call down Tactical Nukes.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanShadowguard.Name: Shadowguard

UmojanWarpingSignatureAcademy.Description: A structure is warping in here from elsewhere.
UmojanWarpingSignatureAcademy.Name: Warping Signature

UmojanEngineeringBay.Description:
Contains upgrades for Umojan infantry and structures.

Enables:
- Anti-Air Turrets from MCSs
- Engineering Tower from MCSs
UmojanEngineeringBay.Name: Mechanics Bay

UmojanBunker.Description:
Defensive structure.
Infantry fights from inside.

Bonus: +1 range to units inside.
UmojanBunker.Name: Bunker

UmojanWarpingSignatureBunker.Description: A structure is warping in here from elsewhere.
UmojanWarpingSignatureBunker.Name: Warping Signature

UmojanAATurret.Description:
Anti-air defensive structure.

Can attack air units.
Detector
UmojanAATurret.Name: Anti-Air Turret

UmojanScienceFacilityGreen.Description:
Contains upgrades for all Umojan Units.

Enables:
- Energy Generator from Supply Cache
- Advanced units at all nearby production facilities
UmojanScienceFacilityGreen.Name: Science Facility

UmojanScienceFacilityBlue.Description:
Contains upgrades for all Umojan Units.

Enables:
- Energy Generator from Supply Cache
- Advanced units at all nearby production facilities
UmojanScienceFacilityBlue.Name: Science Facility

UmojanEngineeringTower.Description: Support defensive structure, can repair nearby mechanical ally and build defensive structures.
UmojanEngineeringTower.Name: Engineering Tower

UmojanEnergyBarricade.Description: Small defensive structure that block movements and vision of ground units.
UmojanEnergyBarricade.Name: Energy Barricade

UmojanSentryGun.Description:
Anti-ground defensive structure. Can burrow to conceal itself.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanSentryGun.Name: Sentry Gun

UmojanSentryGunUnderground.Description:
Anti-ground defensive structure. Can burrow to conceal itself.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanSentryGunUnderground.Name: Sentry Gun

UmojanGhostAcademy.Description:
Contains upgrades for Shadowguards. Can build Nukes for Shadowguards.

Enables:
- Shadowguards at the Academy
UmojanGhostAcademy.Name: Shadow Ops

UmojanFactory.Description:
Vehicle-production facility.

Enables:
- Battlecat
- Norns
- Foundry at the MCSs
UmojanFactory.Name: Workshop

UmojanBattlecat.Description:
Anti-infantry specialist that deals area damage with each attack. Can be mounted by infantry. Can be upgraded to use Blink.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanBattlecat.Name: Battlecat

UmojanBattlecatSpahi.Description:
Anti-infantry specialist that deals area damage with each attack with a Pretorian riding it. Can be upgraded to use Blink

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanBattlecatSpahi.Name: Spahi

UmojanBattlecatCuirassier.Description:
Anti-infantry specialist that deals area damage with each attack with a Plasmabat riding it. Can be upgraded to use Blink

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanBattlecatCuirassier.Name: Cuirassier

UmojanBattlecatLancer.Description:
Anti-infantry specialist that deals area damage with each attack with a Shadowguard riding it. Can be upgraded to use Blink

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanBattlecatLancer.Name: Lancer

UmojanNorns.Description:
Support mech. Can repair mechanical allies and be upgraded to build Energy Barricades, Sentry Guns.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanNorns.Name: Norns

UmojanSpySatellite.Description:
Flying spy. Cloak renders the unit invisible to enemies without detection. Can use Deep Cloak.

Detector
UmojanSpySatellite.Name: Spy Satellite

UmojanBattleTank.Description:
Massive tank. Can switch into Anti-Aerospace Mode to provide long-range anti air support.

Can attack ground units.
Can attack air units if deployed.
UmojanBattleTank.Name: Battle Tank

UmojanBattleTankAA.Description:
Massive anti-air. Can switch into Tank Mode to provide mobile tank support.

Can attack air units.
Can attack ground units if undeployed.
UmojanBattleTankAA.Name: Battle Tank

UmojanWhirlwind.Description:
Slow missile artillery. With the help of a spotter can bombard at extreme range.

Can attack ground units.
UmojanWhirlwind.Name: Whirlwind

UmojanWarpingSignatureWorkshop.Description: A structure is warping in here from elsewhere.
UmojanWarpingSignatureWorkshop.Name: Warping Signature

UmojanArmory.Description:
Contains weapon and armor upgrades for Workshop and Shipyard units.

Enables:
- Battle Tank at the Workshop
- Whirlwind at the Workshop
UmojanArmory.Name: Foundry

UmojanStarport.Description:
Air-unit production facility.

Enables:
- Mist
- Howler
UmojanStarport.Name: Shipyard

UmojanMist.Description:
Support fighter. Loaded with strong anti-capital air missiles. Can be upgraded to be cloaked.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanMist.Name: Mist

UmojanHowler.Description:
Tactical-strike aircraft. Can be upgraded to be cloaked and use Missile Barrage and Missile Burst.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanHowler.Name: Howler

UmojanAloe.Description:
Carrier transport. Loaded with Raptor fighter to attack air targets. Can Heal and switch into Defender Mode to provide increased healing and ground support.

Can attack air units.
UmojanAloe.Name: Aloe

UmojanAloeAG.Description:
Immobile defender. Deals heavy single target damage to ground units. Can Heal and switch into Transport mode to provide air support.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanAloeAG.Name: Aloe

UmojanCrow.Description:
Aerial support unit. Can use Defense Matrix, Recall and can be upgraded to cloak nearby ally units.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanCrow.Name: Crow

UmojanBattleship.Description:
Powerful warship. Can use Stasis Gun and Tactical Jump.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanBattleship.Name: Battleship

UmojanWarpingSignatureShipyard.Description: A structure is warping in here from elsewhere.
UmojanWarpingSignatureShipyard.Name: Warping Signature

UmojanFusionCore.Description:
Contains Battleship, Crow, Aloe and Whirlwind upgrades.

Enables:
- Battleship at the Shipyard
- Crow at the Shipyard
- Frenrir at the Command Hub
UmojanFusionCore.Name: Fleet Core

UmojanFrenrir.Description:
The Frenrir is a massive siege walker capable of leveling entire cities. Can enter siege mode to gain a long range attack.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanFrenrir.Name: Frenrir

UmojanFrenrirFortress.Description:
The Frenrir is a massive siege walker capable of leveling entire cities.

Can attack ground and air units.
UmojanFrenrirFortress.Name: Frenrir

UmojanWarpingSignatureCommandHub.Description: A structure is warping in here from elsewhere.
UmojanWarpingSignatureCommandHub.Name: Warping Signature
